Title: The Grave Shift
Plot: The first day on the job for Dr. Langston turns from bad to worse when a simple burglary case quickly overlaps with a complicated arson and homicide case.
GuestStars: Liz Vassey, David Berman, Michael Cudlitz, Anthony Starke, Michelle Clunie, Victoria Pratt, Darren E. Burrows, Kesun Loder, Marc Vann, Archie Kao, Larry Sullivan, Lisa Arturo, Amy Hathaway
